{
  "stem": "18450.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she, you know, that's the greens.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there nothing to steal there even.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you wanted to steal, you couldn't.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was nothing to steal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] So you had to live like this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the-- I mean the--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The cotton plantation?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the factory in Namagan.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "N-A-M-A-G-A-N.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was walking about an hour.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But over there, it was a lanceman, somebody who was from the same city, and he was there like a watchman.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So natural, we could take out something and sell it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it started being, life was a little better as far as food was concerned.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We suffered, but not as bad as on the plantation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was just, like I said, everybody to me like 90% people died of starvation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But later on in the city, we had already a little bit of food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had wood.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But everything you had to steal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nobody gave you on a platter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had-- we went into-- to the-- the girl who took us in there, she was before on the plantation.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She left earlier.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She took us into her room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We stayed together all the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, it wasn't-- it was one big-- they had a table.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we slept on the table and under the table.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, it wasn't-- it was like a dog, dirt and everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, who cared?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's like you never had a home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's-- that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "From over there, like I said, at least we weren't starving.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Till '46, beginning of '46.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not, not, not exactly, about a year and a half.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they came up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was-- and they said who registered to be from Poland can leave, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
